{"tid":166334,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華：佔中沒有參與施放催淚彈決定","createTime":"2017-03-22T04:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-22T11:35:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"382c30295ef051677687caf4274e832b8d80f32d","tid":166334,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:50:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170322/s00001/8a8aa595ac5cdffb1998ca97fbcb2b56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170322%2Fs00001%2F8a8aa595ac5cdffb1998ca97fbcb2b56.jpg&h=ce77548f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n特首候選人曾俊華接受《眾新聞》及《有線新聞》訪問，在訪問中指自己與特首梁振英關係去到一個點所以辭職，沒有參選佔中時使用催淚彈的決定，另外亦指現屆政府最大敗筆為凡事畫下一條線形成對立。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華在《眾新聞》的訪問中稱，2012年時留任財政司長，因當時有中央人員鼓勵，形容自己「義不容辭」留任。不過他指，「有理由相信」自己並非梁振英的財政司長首選。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華又說，自己並非因參選特首才辭職，而是辭職後才下定決心參選特首。他解釋，2016年底與梁振英不同方面的關係「到了一個點」，認為辭職是最好方法，但不願透露具體原因。他亦指，當時已經完成財政預算案的諮詢及分析工作。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有沒有參與佔中時施放催淚彈的決定，他指沒有參與討論，不知道決策過程中時任政務司長林鄭月娥有沒有參與。他亦在訪問中說，自己有需要為市民對政府的不信任負上一定程度責任。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華在《有線新聞》訪問中就說，現屆政府最大敗筆在於每件事都畫下一條線，形成對立和鬥爭。他表示，如果這條線仍然存在，他沒可能當選。被問到一旦落敗會否呼籲支持者轉而支持勝出的人時，他回應指，3月26日後再交代。"},{"pid":"f5d8b0f18a9e1c9cb9774cc895ada010cbbb16b4","tid":166334,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:51:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170322/s00001/1490156662696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170322%2Fs00001%2F1490156662696&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoNibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=45766b4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170322%2Fs00001%2F1490156662696&h=a8dcc399\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170322/s00001/1490156662696</a>"},{"pid":"56c8aaf02d2cc460efe629093508d71fc94d7891","tid":166334,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:52:58.000Z","msg":"因為根本就無佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8797264bbe07afecc5b06032abc3b686bde484cf","tid":166334,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:43:45.000Z","msg":"睇吓曾生幾鍚住我哋啲身體 曾生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9e83985d9d731e7d2ed9ae3e6722d707cc2598","tid":166334,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:45:22.000Z","msg":"當年傳過鄰國怕689洗哂D錢所以叫財爺留任 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be30cd73bb8b0a7b14d408911a08860afeda4b9","tid":166334,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:47:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad1a0d48cea34da3700b886f7936f4b5998254ce","tid":166334,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:48:04.000Z","msg":"佢好像係少數叫無簽到名的官"},{"pid":"a5133348c39d6705b6a54cb8708288af7437ebb5","tid":166334,"uid":53238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:48:43.000Z","msg":"咁唔滿意而家先嚟辭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\non99"},{"pid":"1de758856b02ceee082cdac3e2e7a79db69a83f2","tid":166334,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:49:52.000Z","msg":"曾聖人 St. John<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33051cbb3bd475e4dc6f10fe5b87945a9fb98796","tid":166334,"uid":2923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁唔滿意而家先嚟辭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\non99</blockquote><br />\n好明顯係689俾中共dq先辭職出黎選啦<img src=\"/assets